<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Ill say this, when most ppl look at a weapon with big damage they relate it to a Warrior only weapon. This is a great weapon for Rangers. Is there a better 2hs out there for them? I dont know. And they get a little mana too. I own this weapon and im a warrior. Would have been nice for a little str of heck maybe some ac value hence the "Defender" in the name. With a measly 152 str i hit for 120, crit for over 200 and cripple for over 300. I know warriors on other posts that have 200+ buffed str that hit for 150,290's,419 (most i have seen posted). /shrug i cant talk smack about the weapon, i love this thing. I dueled a level 44 warrior with fbss, wurmslayer,ssoy. Im 37war with the argent and NO fbss. I nearly killed him. He had around 500 hps left and i 220 or so. We quit there. I crippled him for 250 and he backed off and gacked that a warrior 7 levels under him nearly made him look like a fool /grin.<BR>
